:56:26.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"e83eae813dc71f595f127b403d37fe5d6574dbda","tid":1633616,"uid":223296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:08:18.000Z","msg":"其實勇武手足唔係要退，係要出黎幫幫文宣手足手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[size=４]文宣真係嚴重唔夠人[/size=４]</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">各區連儂牆係咪唔要啦？？我地好聽話唔守，但唔夠人手重建，說好的撕一貼百呢？</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">不分和勇，文宣告急</span></ins></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fea6d8839cd220f5fdc76c394c71fc40ac8fdf05","tid":1633616,"uid":223296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:08:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac18b5db9e484b951f270d0cc0d8f36d31ec3fd3","tid":1633616,"uid":317257,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:10:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"442f6c82f4d3d86945a2944d89a31656a87de385","tid":1633616,"uid":223296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6235bf72f2635031aa500d1a8a2e05f737cca3e1","tid":1633616,"uid":15259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:16:07.000Z","msg":"有時唔洗下下硬打既，轉個方式抗爭都得<br />\n比勇武叉叉電 比文宣組做下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631757\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631757</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:11:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔只比文宣組做下野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係幫同支持文宣組做野<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">不分和勇，文宣告急<br />\n</span></ins></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f569e50e020a5fca63309733a0f6a3fae1f57595","tid":1633616,"uid":220045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac18b5db9e484b951f270d0cc0d8f36d31ec3fd3","tid":1633616,"uid":317257,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:10:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:19:40.000Z","msg":"係佢出post前我已經出左呢個post<br />\n所以我唔係因為佢講d咩去決定我post d野"},{"pid":"42727bad4d2765bd38b402a3433f8d148920cbbd","tid":1633616,"uid":317257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:20:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}